  "title": "Customer Service Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Description:</strong><br>\nWe are looking for enthusiastic and customer-focused individuals to join our retail team. As a Customer Service Associate, you will play a key role in delivering excellent service and creating a pleasant shopping experience for our customers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide friendly and professional service to walk-in customers</li>\n  <li>Upsell and cross-sell products to meet customer needs</li>\n  <li>Replenish and manage store inventory</li>\n  <li>Perform cashier duties and handle transactions accurately</li>\n  <li>Assist in shifting store displays and setting up visual merchandising</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and tidiness of the store, including housekeeping tasks</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum GCE ‘N’ / ‘O’ Levels or ITE qualification</li>\n  <li>No prior experience required (training will be provided)</li>\n  <li>Willing to work on <strong>3 rotating shifts</strong></li>\n  <li>Able to work <strong>5.5 days a week</strong>, including <strong>weekends and Public Holidays</strong></li>\n  <li>Outgoing, well-groomed, and customer service-oriented</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>*Applicants with relevant experience will be considered for Senior Sales position *</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Interested, please Whatspp to 81819562 for more information.</strong></p>",
